                    p Taking this new branding, I created a wide range of digital and print assets, from business cards, pamphlets, letterheads, sponsorship packages, the countless social media graphics, and more. Furthermore, I also wrote copy for all social media graphics as well as the branding guidelines.
                    div(class="flex-wrapper")
